nodes.text: Lorem was a female individual who served the Galactic Empire. Shortly after entering into Imperial service, she was assigned to the probe droid transmission processing unit for Project Swarm, the search for the Rebel Alliance.

Lorem had dark curly hair. She liked to press the boundaries of the dress code, wearing her cap at a jaunty angle. She liked to try to have fun while doing her job, which brought her into conflict with Dirjo Harch.
